{"tid":1724552,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"浸會 POLY 手足 [居安思危 唇亡齒寒]","createTime":"2019-11-15T13:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T13:28:49.000Z","uid":98431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e865419898e1f4e76d921c6cd29cee139002fca0","tid":1724552,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:21:27.000Z","msg":"理大岩岩出左聲明叫人走 同中大狗車到應該有關係<br />\n請即預備後路<br />\n<br />\n狗車暫時退左 <span style=\"color: red;\">但要提防回馬槍 由山徑小路上城</span><br />\n由頭先件事睇得出 群龍無首都唔係辦法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">建議各位可以準備幾個應急方案</span> 物資反而唔緊要 保住手足全身而退先係重點<br />\n<br />\n一守陣 二棄城 三撤退<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">BTW 唔建議死守 但撤之前一定要清除附近指模阿 CCTV記錄等</span></span>"},{"pid":"f10b8d218f4b3f523449f97782cb3dabb0aa54e8","tid":1724552,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:24:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcbfc39a6a1acebe121033c41b338d29ca80382","tid":1724552,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e759a3b8ee297badf4582256fe51059c17df78e","tid":1724552,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n